parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
even when the impact is severe enough to warrant deployment
resulting in injuries to occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays in addressing Takata airbag recalls can leave vehicles on the road with potentially faulty airbags, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Difficulty in scheduling recall repairs
parts availability issues
conflicting information about recall status
and lack of communication from dealerships and manufacturers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the spiral cable can lead to malfunction of critical safety features, including airbags and horns, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Horn failure
airbag malfunction
and other electrical issues related to the spiral cable assembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can prevent the doors from locking or unlocking, which can lead to safety hazards, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: Doors do not lock or unlock remotely
doors can only be opened manually
doors cannot be locked from the outside
keyless entry does not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut down while driving, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle shuts down completely while driving
all dash lights
instrumentation
headlights
and radio shut down
and then restart automatically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear view camera can reduce visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Rear view camera image becomes blurry
shakes rapidly
and static with neon lines appear
making the camera screen view unusable and unreliable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel can cause multiple warning lights to come on randomly, which can be distracting and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Multiple warning lights come on randomly
including ABS
VSC
gas
and check engine lights
speedometer jumps up erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Entune radio/navigation system crashes and stalls while driving
causing safety hazards if the driver has to continually reset the radio power while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rodent damage to the electrical system can cause unexpected failures, leading to safety hazards.
symptoms: Rodents chew through wires
causing electrical system failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to malfunction, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to safety risks in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door locks do not work consistently
the door locks do not respond to the key fob or key
the door locks may not work when inside the vehicle
the door locks may not work in emergency situations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling or hesitation can cause loss of power steering, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or serious injury.
symptoms: The engine hesitates or stalls briefly
the vehicle shudders
the steering becomes difficult
blackish smoke appears from the rearview mirror
loud sounds and grinding noises are heard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the navigation system and radio can cause distractions while driving, which can lead to accidents or serious injury.
symptoms: The navigation system and radio stop working for a few seconds
the system restarts but requires reentry of navigation data
the problem worsens over time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of Takata airbags can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: None reported
but the vehicle has an active recall for Takata airbags.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Frame and Radiator Support Cross Member Rust
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the frame and radiator support cross member can cause structural damage to the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or serious injury.
symptoms: None reported
but the vehicle has rust damage to the frame and radiator support cross member.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of mold and mildew odor can cause health issues for occupants.
symptoms: A mildew odor is present inside the vehicle
occupants become ill.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents or serious injury.
symptoms: The vehicle continues to reverse backwards when shifted into drive
the vehicle crashes into an object.
